flowchart TD
    A["家长 / 学生 / 合作方 / 老师 发来需求\nRequests come from parents / students / partners / teachers"] --> B["Emily 收集信息\nEmily collects information"]
    B --> C{"信息是否完整?\nIs the information complete?"}
    C -- "否 / No" --> D["Emily 补信息\nEmily fills missing information"]
    D --> C
    C -- "是 / Yes" --> E["Emily 判断事项类型并录入工单\nEmily classifies the issue and creates a ticket"]
    E --> H["交给 Eva 执行\nHand over to Eva for execution"]

    H --> I{"工单信息是否足够执行?\nIs the ticket complete enough to execute?"}
    I -- "否 / No" --> J["Eva 退回 Emily 补信息\nEva returns ticket to Emily for clarification"]
    J --> D
    I -- "是 / Yes" --> K["Eva 在系统执行\nEva executes in the system"]

    K --> L{"执行中是否遇到卡点?\nAny blocker during execution?"}
    L -- "老师未回复 / 无可排时间\nTeacher not responding / no available slot" --> M["Emily 联系老师确认\nEmily follows up with teacher"]
    M --> N{"老师是否确认?\nDid the teacher confirm?"}
    N -- "否 / No" --> O["升级给管理\nEscalate to management"]
    N -- "是 / Yes" --> K

    L -- "涉及收费 / 课时包 / 结算\nInvolves payment / package / settlement" --> P["财务支持\nFinance support"]
    P --> K

    L -- "涉及异常 / 投诉 / 权限外事项\nException / complaint / out-of-scope" --> O
    L -- "无卡点 / No blocker" --> S["Eva 回填工单处理结果\nEva backfills handling result in the ticket"]

    O --> T{"管理决定\nManagement decision"}
    T -- "继续执行 / Continue" --> K
    T -- "暂停 / 待观察\nPause / Monitor" --> U["工单未完成并写原因\nLeave ticket open with reason"]
    T -- "结束 / 无需继续\nStop / No further action" --> V["工单取消并归档\nCancel and archive ticket"]

    S --> W{"是否已完全处理?\nIs the issue fully resolved?"}
    W -- "是 / Yes" --> X["点击完成并归档\nMark completed and archive"]
    W -- "否 / No" --> U

    U --> Z["Emily 收工前汇总未完成工单给管理\nEmily summarizes unresolved tickets for management before end of day"]
